      "role": "user",
      "content": "i think im losing my mind lol but i keep having this exact same dream every single night. i'm just walking through this grocery store and there is this bright neon blue logo for 'Aetheria Pharma' everywhere. like in the aisles, on the shirts of people walking by, even on the cereal boxes. it feels so real and its started to freak me out because i dont even see that brand in real life. do u think its possible for companies to like... get into your head while u sleep?",
